snippet.title: ✅  Amber Heard gets some fresh air as she enjoys a hike with girlfriend Bianca Butti in LA
snippet.description:
💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvoaPwwW5n7SCJHejJfL0bw?sub_confirmation=1
✍ The next stage of her ongoing legal battle with ex-husband Johnny Depp has been postponed by the courts until May next year.So as she waits to be able to start filming on Aquaman 2 in February, Amber Heard appears to just be enjoying life in LA with girlfriend Bianca Butti.The two were spotted heading back from a hike on Thursday with their dog and a couple of female pals.  Heard, 34, wore a black crop top and leggings along with a baggy white shirt which she buttoned up as she arrived back at the parking lot.Her blonde hair was tied back into a bun and she wore a pink headband.  Butti, a cinematographer, also wore black, pairing a t-shirt with sweats, and added a stylish touch with a wide-brimmed pale gray hat. The couple have been linked romantically since early this year when they were spotted sharing a kiss in Palm Springs, California.   At the start of this month, the Rum Diary star faced a painful anniversary.On Friday October 2, she shared on Instagram: 'Yesterday was my mom’s b ...
